Salaryman ga Isekai ni Ittara Shitennou ni Natta Hanashi

In an alternate fantasy world, the Demon King reigns with a formidable army led by his Four Heavenly Kings. One happens to be Uchimura Denosuke, a normal salaryman unexpectedly plucked from his mundane life by the Demon King himself. But even in this new realm, Uchimura is bestowed no particular powers. Can he survive treacherous missions with only the knowledge of an office worker?
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Ikidaore mo Dekinai Konna Isekai ja
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

Sumire was a high school girl before she leapt into another world the moment she fell down. Before she could collapse and die, she came across a silver-haired boy who had already collapsed and was dying. One thing led to another and she ended up working at an Adventurer’s Guild. She doesn’t have any special powers, but she’s well liked by strange plants and animals. What does Sumire’s future hold?!
(Kono Sekai wa Mou Ore ga Sukutte Tomi to Kenryoku wo Te ni Iretashi, Onna Kishi ya Onna Maou to Shiro de Tanoshiku Kurashiteru kara, Ore Igai no Yuusha wa) Mou Isekai ni Konaide Kudasai.

[Question] A new different world hero appeared on Horizon [Answer] Turn back to Earth right now!
After the struggle, I saved the other world and tried to enjoy the rest of my life freely. But for some reason, the incarnating hero from the earth will spring up here on the Horizon. Don't be silly! This world is mine!
The Holy Knight, the Demon Girl, the Elves, the Beastmen, and even the ordinary people, everything in this world will never be given to anyone!
NEET? Izakaya? SDF? No matter who the enemy is! Other-hero, turn back to the Earth!
Drive back all the other world hero with wisdom, courage and perfection, a slapstick fantasy opens!
(Source: Kadokawa, translated)
